South African Sugar Association Cuts Crop Forecast to 1.909 Million Tons

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-03-28T10:00:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-28/south-african-sugar-association-cuts-crop-forecast-to-1-909-million-tons.html
The South African Sugar Association
cut its crop forecast to 1.909 million metric tons from 1.911
million tons a month ago, it said on its website today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  